.TH "vmw_bo_acc_size" 9 "vmw_bo_acc_size" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
vmw_bo_acc_size \- Calculate the pinned memory usage of buffers
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "size_t" vmw_bo_acc_size
.BI "(struct vmw_private *dev_priv "  ","
.BI "size_t size "  ","
.BI "bool user "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev_priv" 12
Pointer to a struct vmw_private identifying the device.
.IP "size" 12
The requested buffer size.
.IP "user" 12
Whether this is an ordinary dma buffer or a user dma buffer.
